** μ-{{link-en|芋螺毒素|conotoxin}}
** δ-{{link-en|atracotoxin|atracotoxin}}<ref name=Grolleau_2000>{{cite journal |author=Grolleau F, Stankiewicz M, Birinyi-Strachan L, Wang XH, Nicholson GM, Pelhate M, Lapied B |title=Electrophysiological analysis of the neurotoxic action of a funnel-web spider toxin, delta-atracotoxin-HV1a, on insect voltage-gated Na<sup>+</sup> channels |journal=J. Exp. Biol. |volume=204 |issue=Pt 4 |pages=711–21 |year=2001 |pmid=11171353}}</ref>
